{"tid":1423571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"言語藝術戰略","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:44:38.000Z","uid":189670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20dfb573ad4f76f464e8e76e00380c13bd393a80","tid":1423571,"uid":189670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"運動巳去到危急存亡之時，好易重蹈反佔中覆轍，每個細節都要好小心<br />\n每次被扣帽子好蝕，何不work hard, play smart<br />\n<br />\n口号例子：<br />\n1） 愛國愛港反港獨<br />\n5大訴求，缺一不可。。。。<br />\n<br />\n2）愛國愛港，拒絕XX條例<br />\n3）當有人鬧你攪亂香港，你可以鬧佢&quot;你係未愛國架？你攪亂國家呀&quot;<br />\n<br />\n類似係咁上下，要立於不敗之地<br />\n古有臥薪嘗膽，忍辱負重<br />\n<br />\n被免字詞：<br />\n反<br />\n革命<br />\n光復<br />\n<br />\n改為：<br />\n潔淨<br />\n改革"},{"pid":"b223aa868533674a2f74e8773d6d71f92b57ed79","tid":1423571,"uid":189670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:22:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98d81b98deb4627e1e299c6fa7473321eefd8df8","tid":1423571,"uid":189670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"651e427e034789d925e1a16e2b0585d7f64a77f4","tid":1423571,"uid":189670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cb7aeed7c53b93896b2817d59e0513427d97d7b","tid":1423571,"uid":189670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6337b4549ec92681c1b01c170ec10d8bb6603f0","tid":1423571,"uid":189670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:24:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7b5c298738206c262f307b6c72b275960d046eb","tid":1423571,"uid":189670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d69dccc67f357a1e80f9544d7da6909c74265adf","tid":1423571,"uid":189670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48a6f6adc3ab2c3cdbc0138e329761ab9c6d9f7b","tid":1423571,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s